{"type":"step-attempt","step":"spec-review","sessionId":"7e31244a-eca4-4ca4-9264-cb6a8b04a779","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/cancel-canceled-dir/spec-review-result-001.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":true,"findings":[{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/cancel-canceled-dir/tasks.md","title":"T-04: null return from evacuateChangeFolder not explicitly handled for persist step","rationale":"T-03 says 'warn and return safely' when slug is empty, but does not specify the return type (null/undefined). T-04 then passes the result as `canceledDirAbs` to `new JobStateStore(..., { changeDir: canceledDirAbs })`. If changeDir is null/undefined, JobStateStore.getStateJsonPath() throws (requires slug+stateRoot or changeDir). T-04 should explicitly state: if evacuateChangeFolder returns null, skip the canceled persist step as well."},{"severity":"low","resolution":"fixable","file":"specrunner/changes/cancel-canceled-dir/tasks.md","title":"T-06: cancelAllTerminated worktree detection dependency not documented","rationale":"T-06 refactors makeJob to write state into a worktree-only layout. JobStateStore.list() detects worktrees by scanning <repoRoot>/.git/specrunner-worktrees/. For cancelAllTerminated tests to keep finding jobs, makeJob's worktreeDir must be buildWorktreePath(tempDir, slug, jobId) (which resolves to tempDir/.git/specrunner-worktrees/<slug>-<jobId8>). This dependency is implicit and should be documented in T-06 to prevent implementers from using an arbitrary temp path that list() cannot discover."}],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/store/job-state-store.ts","title":"changeDir seam already exists — no new API needed for D3","rationale":"JobStateStore constructor already accepts opts.changeDir (line 156-162), and getStateJsonPath()/getEventsPath() already prioritize changeDir over slug-convention paths (lines 168-194). D3's implementation requires no new interface additions."},{"severity":"low","file":"src/store/job-state-store.ts","title":"D7 archive-skip target line confirmed — one-line change","rationale":"The skip condition `entry.name === 'archive'` is at line 225. Adding `|| entry.name === 'canceled'` is the complete change required for D7.","line":225}]},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-06-27T00:40:13.602Z","endedAt":"2026-06-27T00:44:13.902Z"}
